Mrs. Jessy teaches her 7-year-old daughter to tell the day of a week when Jessy tells a number between 1 to 7.  Implement this scenario and generate an algorithm for the same.

Answer text


Start the program.
Create String array of length 7.
Initialize the array with Sunday, Monday...Saturday from 0...6.
Get the day of the week.
if 0<day of the week<8, then display array[day of the week - 1].
else display Invalid.
Stop.
